ComicInfo.Title: The Power of Pluto!; Aftermath!
ComicInfo.Summary:
The Power of Pluto!: Thor recovers from his injuries last issue and goes looking for a rematch with Hercules who has been tricked into signing a contract with Pluto.
Aftermath!: The tale of Ragnarok reveals Loki as the cause.
